MLUMH.PA.long_name: Union Metallurgique de la Haute-Seine S.A.
MLUMH.PA.summary: Union Metallurgique de la Haute-Seine S.A. distributes general hardware products, machinery and equipment. It distributes products, such as machinery, tools, electrical appliances, plumbing fixtures, heating equipment, steel products. The company was founded in 1921 and is based in Melun, France.
